---
import Layout from '@/layouts/Layout.astro';
import { useTranslations } from '@/i18n/utils';

export function getStaticPaths() {
  return [
    { params: { lang: 'en' } },
    { params: { lang: 'es' } }
  ];
}

const { lang } = Astro.params as { lang: 'en' | 'es' };
const t = useTranslations(lang);

const article = {
  en: {
    title: 'My First Ayahuasca Ceremony with Master Dan',
    excerpt: 'The extraordinary account of my first ceremony with Master Dan Reynolds, where I experienced a complete transformation into a black jaguar and witnessed ancestral rituals that forever changed my understanding of the shamanic world.',
    date: '2025-10-02',
    author: 'Maestro Denis',
    authorBio: 'Master healer with over 15 years of experience in Amazonian ancestral medicine.',
    image: '/img/first-ayahuasca-ceremony-between-denis-and-dan.webp',
    readTime: '15 min',
    category: 'Experiences',
    tags: ['ayahuasca', 'ceremony', 'transformation', 'jaguar', 'shamanism', 'dan reynolds', 'vision', 'amazon']
  },
  es: {
    title: 'Mi Primera Ceremonia de Ayahuasca con el Maestro Dan',
    excerpt: 'El relato extraordinario de mi primera ceremonia con el Maestro Dan Reynolds, donde experimenté una transformación completa en jaguar negro y presencié rituales ancestrales que cambiaron mi comprensión del mundo chamánico para siempre.',
    date: '2025-10-02',
    author: 'Maestro Denis',
    authorBio: 'Maestro curandero con más de 15 años de experiencia en medicina ancestral amazónica.',
    image: '/blog/primera-ceremonia-dan.webp',
    readTime: '15 min',
    category: 'Experiencias',
    tags: ['ayahuasca', 'ceremonia', 'transformación', 'jaguar', 'chamanismo', 'dan reynolds', 'visión', 'amazonia']
  }
};

const currentArticle = article[lang as keyof typeof article];
---

<Layout 
  title={`${currentArticle.title} | Blog Casa del Jaguar`}
  description={currentArticle.excerpt}
  keywords={currentArticle.tags.join(', ')}
>
  <main>
    <article class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 md:px-8 py-16 -mt-16 pt-24">
      <nav class="text-sm text-gray-600 mb-8">
        <a href={lang === 'en' ? '/en' : '/'} class="hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">
          {lang === 'en' ? 'Home' : 'Inicio'}
        </a>
        <span class="mx-2">›</span>
        <a href={lang === 'en' ? '/en/blog' : '/blog'} class="hover:text-brand-primary transition-colors">Blog</a>
        <span class="mx-2">›</span>
        <span class="text-brand-dark">{currentArticle.category}</span>
      </nav>

      <div class="mb-6">
        <span class="bg-brand-primary text-brand-dark px-4 py-2 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">
          {currentArticle.category}
        </span>
      </div>

      <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mb-6 leading-tight">
        {currentArticle.title}
      </h1>

      <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center text-gray-600 mb-8 space-x-6">
        <div class="flex items-center space-x-2">
          <div class="w-10 h-10 bg-brand-light rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="text-brand-dark font-bold text-sm">{currentArticle.author.charAt(0)}</span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class="font-medium text-brand-dark">{currentArticle.author}</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">{currentArticle.authorBio}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="text-sm">
          <p>{new Date(currentArticle.date).toLocaleDateString(lang === 'en' ? 'en-US' : 'es-ES', { 
            year: 'numeric', 
            month: 'long', 
            day: 'numeric' 
          })}</p>
          <p>{currentArticle.readTime} {lang === 'en' ? 'read' : 'de lectura'}</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mb-12">
        <img 
          src={currentArticle.image}
          alt={currentArticle.title}
          class="w-full h-98 object-cover rounded-xl shadow-lg"
        />
      </div>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        {lang === 'en' ? (
          <>
            <p class="scroll-animate text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 font-gotham leading-relaxed">
              Upon arriving at the ceremony location, to our surprise, Dan was not alone; he was with other tourists. I heard him say: "Hey, David, this is the person I was telling you about."
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Discovering that Master Dan spoke about me with other people</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              This person looked at me intently and said: "Well, I sense a strong connection and energy within him." Dan and David didn't speak Spanish, so they weren't concerned about paying attention to what they were saying, since my wife didn't understand English.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Only I could understand it, but I said nothing. Instead, I mentally thought: "Another crazy thing."
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              The ceremonial maloca was beautiful and very well maintained. While Dan explained the protocol and process that would unfold during the ceremony, I realized that this master conducted his ceremonies completely differently from my experience at 16 years old.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3">Dosage is very important in a Ceremony</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-800">
                A very small dose compared to my first experience, which reassured me greatly. Although Dan told me: "The Ayahuasca I prepare is very potent, you don't need much quantity and it tastes quite good."
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              When he mentioned the taste, it reminded me of the horrible taste of my past experience, but knowing that this ayahuasca tasted good helped me a lot.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              This time, I knew that after taking ayahuasca, the effects take about 20 minutes to appear. So I was patient and this time I sat in a rocking chair instead of on the floor.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Dan conducted the inaugural ceremony; everything was very beautiful until it came time to take the medicine. I did so, and the taste was very pleasant. Dan wasn't lying.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">High Technology in an Ayahuasca Ceremony</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              After taking the medicine, Dan told me he would use a technology called Hemi-Sync, which helps the brain reach a state of effortless concentration. That's what Dan told me.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              In my mind, I thought: "What a strange shaman, using modern technology combined with rituals." I closed my eyes and began to listen to the sound.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              It actually brought me a sense of calm that made me feel sleepy and I began to yawn several times.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">The Good Begins</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              After about 20 minutes, I heard a sound and opened my eyes. When I did, I found myself running. I was running very fast and didn't understand what was happening.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I saw myself in the middle of the Amazon jungle. It was night, with a beautiful full moon illuminating the forest.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              In my mind, I kept repeating: "Stop running. Where am I going? Denis, stop! Why are you running?" In those moments, I realized that either the grass was very close to my face, or my face was very close to the ground.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Another thing that surprised me was that I wanted to look at the night sky, but I couldn't do it like humans normally do by tilting their head back to see the sky without any problem.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I simply couldn't and it wasn't something that physically prevented me; I simply felt it as a physical limitation while running.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-purple-800 italic">
                Mentally, I wondered: "What's happening? What am I doing in the middle of the jungle? Where is everyone? Where is my wife?"
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I kept asking myself all those questions, but I kept running. Finally, I could see, hear and smell fire, as if someone had started a fire and was burning plants or wood many meters away.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I said: "What's happening?"
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Several minutes passed until I reached a point in the forest where there was no grass. This area looked as if someone had cultivated it. Upon arriving, I stopped and, at that moment, I said: "I want to get up," but my body didn't obey me.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              It was then that I looked at my arms and to my amazement, they weren't arms; they were the paws of a feline.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Being Inside a Black Jaguar</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I looked at my hands and saw they had claws. The color of my skin wasn't that of a person; it was that of a black-furred feline with spots, which I could see clearly under the moonlight.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-amber-800 font-semibold italic text-lg">
                "A wave of fear invaded me and I told myself: I must quickly head to where that fire is, since it's a sign of civilization. There must be people there who will know what's happening to me and will surely help me."
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I ran harder, feeling relieved to see that I was approaching the fire. However, my relief was short-lived, as the bonfire wasn't at my level; I seemed to be in an elevated area.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I approached cautiously to see what was happening, as I began to hear voices but couldn't understand what they were saying.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              As I got closer, I saw a group of five natives gathered around the bonfire. They had made the fire near the riverbank and the water level had dropped, so I found myself on elevated ground.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I felt about 5 minutes passed and one of the natives who was sitting stood up and walked around the campfire until positioning himself in front of his companions.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              In his right hand he held a piece of a branch. I wondered what this person would do.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Using the branch like a pencil, he began to write something on the ground. It was a combination of symbols and something resembling letters.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Honestly, I was stunned and thought: "What is he writing?" My vision was so sharp that when I wanted to see something closer, it was as if my eyes had a zoom effect.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              After finishing writing, he quickly moved to stand next to one of his companions and all five began making some strange sounds.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Witnessing something incredible</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              They seemed to know that something was about to happen, as I could see joy in their expressions. I thought: "They're calling someone or something."
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I felt a tingling on my skin and seconds after he wrote, I felt a very strong energy accumulating and over the bonfire, this energy began to accumulate, forming a cloud of smoke.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              With each passing second, it became denser and denser. Then, I heard the sound of thunder and something emerged from that cloud of smoke.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I was petrified, watching what was happening.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-green-800 font-semibold">
                When all the smoke disappeared, my surprise was great because before my eyes was a gigantic being in front of the natives. This being had feline characteristics, black with dark spots, standing on two legs, a humanoid jaguar.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              The natives were ecstatic, four of them danced around, while the one who wrote on the ground was kneeling before this being.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I couldn't understand what I was seeing. I was so amazed that I wanted to see in more detail, but I didn't want them to know I was there.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Next to me was a tree with a considerably large branch, so I decided to climb up there and observe from above.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              That's exactly what I did, very slowly and without making noise, or so I thought.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Indeed. With a single jump, I found myself on that branch, delighted that, from what I could see, no one had noticed my presence.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Feeling the Power of the Gaze</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I resumed observation and saw how this being was giving instructions to the natives until something very strange happened.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              This being looked up at me and we made eye contact.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              But his gaze pierced through my mind. I saw how his feline eyes enlarged, only his eyes, and when I tried to resist, I felt as if something or someone was pushing me.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              This caused me to fall from the tree and a bit of fear invaded me.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Then I had to turn around, trying to return by the same path, but I couldn't find the way back to my group.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I only remember having re-entered the jungle with very thick undergrowth.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Then I opened my eyes again and this time I found myself back in the ceremonial maloca.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I saw my wife next to me and then Dan asked me how I felt. I told him I still felt dizzy and connected.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I didn't vomit, but something strange happened when I tried to get up from the chair; I couldn't.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              I felt my legs as if they weighed a ton. So, following Dan's recommendation, I waited a bit longer before going to my room.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-brand-light border-l-4 border-brand-primary p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-brand-dark font-semibold italic text-lg">
                That night I learned many things about the shamanic world, debunking myths and discarding lies that unfortunately still exist to this day.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              This first ceremony with Master Dan marked a before and after in my understanding of sacred medicine. The experience of transforming into a black jaguar was not just a vision, but an awakening to my true spiritual nature and my ancestral connection with the feline realm.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              The encounter with the humanoid jaguar being and the rituals of the natives showed me that there exists a parallel world of knowledge and wisdom that transcends our ordinary understanding. That night I understood that my path as a healer was just beginning.
            </p>
          </>
        ) : (
          <>
            <p class="scroll-animate text-xl text-gray-700 mb-8 font-gotham leading-relaxed">
              Al llegar al lugar de la ceremonia, para nuestra sorpresa, Dan no estaba solo; estaba con otros turistas. Le oí decir: «Oye, David, esta es la persona de la que te hablaba».
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Descubriendo que el Maestro Dan habló de mí con otras personas</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Esta persona me miró fijamente y dijo: «Bien, siento una fuerte conexión y energía dentro de él». Dan y David no hablaban español, así que no se preocuparon por prestar atención a lo que decían, ya que mi esposa no entendía inglés.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Solo yo pude entenderlo, pero no dije nada. En cambio, mentalmente pensé: «Otra locura».
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              La maloca ceremonial era hermosa y estaba muy bien cuidada. Mientras Dan me explicaba el protocolo y el proceso que se desarrollaría durante la ceremonia, me di cuenta de que este maestro dirigía sus ceremonias de forma completamente diferente a mi experiencia a los 16 años.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-blue-50 border-l-4 border-blue-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-blue-800 mb-3">La dosis es muy importante en una Ceremonia</h3>
              <p class="text-blue-800">
                Una dosis muy pequeña en comparación con mi primera experiencia, lo cual me tranquilizó mucho. Aunque Dan me dijo: «La Ayahuasca que preparo es muy potente, no se necesita mucha cantidad y sabe bastante bien».
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Cuando mencionó el sabor, me recordó el horrible sabor de mi experiencia pasada, pero saber que esta ayahuasca tenía buen sabor me ayudó mucho.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Esta vez, sabía que después de tomar ayahuasca, los efectos tardan unos 20 minutos en aparecer. Así que fui paciente y esta vez me senté en una mecedora en lugar de en el suelo.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Dan dirigió la ceremonia inaugural; todo era muy hermoso hasta que llegó el momento de tomar la medicina. Así lo hice, y el sabor era muy agradable. Dan no mentía.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Alta tecnología en una Ceremonia de Ayahuasca</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Después de tomar la medicina, Dan me dijo que usaría una tecnología llamada Hemi-Sync, que ayuda al cerebro a alcanzar un estado de concentración sin esfuerzo. Eso fue lo que me dijo Dan.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              En mi mente, pensé: «Qué chamán tan extraño, usando tecnología moderna combinada con rituales». Cerré los ojos y comencé a escuchar el sonido.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              En realidad me trajo una sensación de calma que me hizo sentir sueño y comencé a bostezar varias veces.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Lo Bueno Comienza</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Después de unos 20 minutos, oí un sonido y abrí los ojos. Al hacerlo, me encontré corriendo. Corría muy rápido y no entendía qué pasaba.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Me vi en medio de la selva amazónica. Era de noche, con una hermosa luna llena iluminando la selva.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              En mi mente, me repetía: «Deja de correr. ¿Adónde voy? ¡Denis, detente! ¿Por qué corres?». En esos momentos, me di cuenta de que o la hierba estaba muy cerca de mi cara, o mi cara estaba muy cerca del suelo.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Otra cosa que me sorprendió fue que quería mirar el cielo nocturno, pero no podía hacerlo como normalmente lo hacen los humanos inclinando la cabeza hacia atrás para ver el cielo sin ningún problema.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Simplemente no pude y no era algo que me lo impidiera físicamente; simplemente lo sentí como una limitación física al correr.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-purple-50 border-l-4 border-purple-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-purple-800 italic">
                Mentalmente, me preguntaba: «¿Qué pasa? ¿Qué hago en medio de la selva? ¿Dónde están todos? ¿Dónde está mi esposa?».
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Me seguía haciendo todas esas preguntas, pero seguí corriendo. Finalmente, pude ver, oír y oler fuego, como si alguien hubiera provocado un incendio y estuviera quemando plantas o leña a muchos metros de distancia.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Dije: «¿Qué pasa?».
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Pasaron varios minutos hasta que llegué a un punto en el bosque donde no había hierba. Esta zona parecía como si alguien la hubiera cultivado. Al llegar, me detuve y, en ese momento, dije: «Quiero levantarme», pero mi cuerpo no me obedeció.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Fue entonces cuando miré mis brazos y para mi asombro, no eran brazos; eran las patas de un felino.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Estar dentro de un Jaguar Negro</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Miré mis manos y vi que tenían garras. El color de mi piel no era el de una persona; era la de un felino de pelaje negro con manchas, que podía ver claramente bajo la luz de la luna.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-amber-50 border-l-4 border-amber-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-amber-800 font-semibold italic text-lg">
                «Una ola de miedo me invadió y me dije: Debo dirigirme rápidamente al lugar donde está ese fuego, ya que es una señal de civilización. Debe haber gente ahí que sabrá lo que me pasa y seguramente me ayudará.»
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Corrí con más fuerza, sintiéndome aliviado al ver que me acercaba al fuego. Sin embargo, mi alivio duró poco, ya que la hoguera no estaba a mi altura; Yo parecía estar en una zona elevada.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Me acerqué con cautela para ver qué pasaba, pues comencé a escuchar voces pero no podía entender lo que decían.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Al acercarme, vi a un grupo de cinco nativos reunidos alrededor de la hoguera. Habían hecho el fuego cerca de la orilla del río y el nivel del mismo había bajado, por lo que me encontré en un terreno elevado.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Sentí que pasaron unos 5 minutos y uno de los nativos que estaba sentado se levantó y caminó alrededor de la fogata hasta posicionarse frente a sus compañeros.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              En su mano derecha sostenía un pedazo de una rama. Me pregunté qué haría esta persona.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Con la rama a modo de lápiz, empezó a escribir algo en el suelo. Era una combinación de símbolos y algo parecido a letras.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Sinceramente, me quedé atónito y pensé: «¿Qué escribe?». Mi vista era tan aguda que, cuando quería ver algo más de cerca, era como si mis ojos tuvieran un efecto zoom.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Después de terminar de escribir, rápidamente se movió para pararse al lado de uno de sus compañeros y los cinco comenzaron a hacer algunos sonidos extraños.
            </p>

            <h2 class="scroll-animate text-3xl font-bold text-brand-dark font-georgia mt-12 mb-6">Presenciando algo increíble</h2>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Parecían saber que algo estaba a punto de suceder, pues podía ver alegría en sus expresiones. Pensé: «Están llamando a alguien o a algo».
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Sentí un hormigueo en la piel y segundos después de que escribió, sentí una energía muy fuerte acumulándose y sobre el fuego de la hoguera, esta energía comenzó a acumularse, formando una nube de humo.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Con cada segundo que pasaba, se hacía más y más denso. Entonces, oí el sonido de un trueno y algo emergió de aquella nube de humo.
            </p>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Estaba petrificado, mirando lo que estaba pasando.
            </p>

            <div class="scroll-animate bg-green-50 border-l-4 border-green-400 p-6 mb-8">
              <p class="text-green-800 font-semibold">
                Cuando todo el humo desapareció, mi sorpresa fue grande porque ante mis ojos se encontraba un ser gigantesco frente a los nativos. Este ser tenía características felinas, de color negro con manchas oscuras, de pie sobre dos patas, un jaguar humanoide.
              </p>
            </div>

            <p class="scroll-animate mb-6">
              Los nativos estaban extasiados, cuatro de ellos danzaban alrededor, mientras el que escribió en el suelo estaba arrodillado frente a este ser.
